
<sellerabr>ALLIED-SIGNAL</sellerabr> {<sellercode>ALD</sellercode>} TO SELL LINOTYPE UNIT
    MORRIS TOWNSHIP, N.J., March 25 - <seller>Allied-Signal Inc</seller> said it
<status>agreed to sell</status> its <acquired>Linotype Group</acquired> unit to {<purchaser>Commerzbank AG</purchaser>}
