    <sellerabr>Allied-Signal</sellerabr> said <purchabr>Commerzbank</purchabr> is expected to offer shares
of the unit to the public later this year.
    The company said the agreement is subject to approval by
the government and its shareholders.
    The <acqabr>Linotype</acqabr> unit, based in <acqloc>Eschborn, West Germany</acqloc>, had
